<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="home-section yuyun-page" aria-labelledby="yuyun-page-title">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <p class="section-heading__eyebrow">余韵</p>
    <h2 id="yuyun-page-title" class="section-heading__title">古今相接 · 时光文创</h2>
  </div>

  <p class="section-intro">
    以计时器物为灵感，构建具有时间感与物件诗意的文创作品。
  </p>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card__illustration">
        <img class="feature-card__image" src="/images/site/chizi.svg" alt="《时尺》工具图鉴 占位图" />
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card__meta">
        <span>文具套装</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="feature-card__title">《时尺》工具图鉴</h3>
      <p class="feature-card__subtitle">圭表测影知方寸，晷针移影刻光阴</p>
      <p class="feature-card__text">
        一套匠心文具，将古代计时器皿与刻度观象融入笔记、尺规与印章，伴随书写与时间的节律。
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card__illustration">
        <img class="feature-card__image" src="/images/site/mingxinpian.svg" alt="《光阴十二刻》明信片套装 占位图" />
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card__meta">
        <span>明信片套装</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="feature-card__title">《光阴十二刻》</h3>
      <p class="feature-card__subtitle">十二时辰对应十二种计时器，黑色细绳捆扎，蜡封印章</p>
      <p class="feature-card__text">
        以文字与图像记录钟表、漏刻、星象等十二种计时器，打造可触可藏的时光册页。
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card__illustration">
        <img class="feature-card__image" src="/images/site/xiang.svg" alt="守时线香礼盒 占位图" />
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card__meta">
        <span>香篆礼盒</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="feature-card__title">守时线香礼盒</h3>
      <p class="feature-card__subtitle">十二时辰对应草木香气，焚一支知光阴</p>
      <p class="feature-card__text">
        选用草木与香篆，以时间节点对应独特香气，生成每日仪式感与古意定时的氛围。
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card__illustration">
        <img class="feature-card__image" src="/images/site/moxing.svg" alt="水运仪象拼装模型 占位图" />
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card__meta">
        <span>拼装模型</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="feature-card__title">水运仪象拼装模型</h3>
      <p class="feature-card__subtitle">木质机械传动，再现宋代天文钟智慧</p>
      <p class="feature-card__text">
        以木质零件与齿轮复原古代天文钟机构，呈现水力驱动与机械节律的匠心再造。
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
